# Accles & Pollock

> Manufacturer of precision manipulated tube assemblies for aerospace, defence and other high-integrity applications.

## What they do

Accles & Pollock manufactures low-volume, precision manipulated tube assemblies for high-integrity applications across the aerospace, defence, automotive and nuclear sectors. Based in the West Midlands, the company offers tube manipulation, CNC machining, assembly and testing, with components supplied with full product traceability. The business traces its origins to 1896.

## Products and solutions

- **Tube assemblies** - rigid and flexible pipes, ducts, tube coils, convoluted tube, fuel fillers and structural assemblies in materials including stainless steel, nickel alloys, inconel and titanium.
- **Fluid management systems** - bespoke tubular products for high-specification applications.

## Frameworks, accreditations and memberships

- **Frameworks:** JOSCAR (achieved 2024)
- **Accreditations:** AS9100, ISO 9001, ISO 14001, NADCAP for welding and brazing, IATF 16949
- **Memberships:** ADS Group, Midlands Aerospace Alliance

